headline: Gear Up for Hologic (HOLX) Q4 Earnings: Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Hologic (HOLX), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended September 2025.
